\c 29
\s inzwi raJehovha
\p
\v 1 Ipai, Jehovha, imwi vanakomana vaMwari, ipai Jehovha kudzo nesimba.
\v 2 Ipai Jehovha kudzo yakafanirwa nezita rake; namatai kuna Jehovha nenguvo tsvene.
\p
\v 3 Inzwi raJehovha riri pamusoro pemvura zhinji; Mwari wokubwinya unotinhira, iye Jehovha ari pamusoro pemvura zhinji-zhinji.
\v 4 Inzwi raJehovha rine simba; inzwi raJehovha rizere noumambo.
\v 5 Inzwi raJehovha rinovhuna misidhari; zvirokwazvo, Jehovha anovhunanya misidhari yeRebhanoni.
\v 6 Anoipemberesa semhuru; iro Rebhanoni neSirioni semhuru yenyati.
\v 7 Inzwi raJehovha rinopamura mirazvo yomoto.
\v 8 Inzwi raJehovha rinodederesa renje; Jehovha anodederesa renje reKadheshi.
\v 9 Inzwi raJehovha rinoberekesa nondo, rinosvuura miti yamatondo; nomutemberi yake zvese zvinoti: Kubwinya.
\p
\v 10 Jehovha akagara pachigaro choushe paboporodzi remvura; zvirokwazvo, Jehovha anogara ari mambo nokusingaperi.
\v 11 Jehovha achapa vanhu vake simba; Jehovha acharopafadza vanhu vake nerugare.
